<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<data>
	<father name="death">
		<gather name="肉鸽地图">
			<level name="deathMode">
				<info enemyLv="10" modeDiy="death" noTreasureB="1" noAIB="1" overWarn="退出后，等你再次回来时，你将回到进入当前大地图时的最初状态。" />
				<drop noB="1"/>
				<sceneLabel>WoTu</sceneLabel>
				<unitG>
					<unitOrder id="enemy1" camp="enemy">
						<numberType>pro</numberType>
					</unitOrder>
				</unitG>
				
				<eventG>
					<group id="groupFail">
						<event id="e_fail">
							<condition delay="2">bodyEvent:die; allPlayerCtrl</condition>
							<order>deathP1Die</order>
						</event>
					</group>
				</eventG>
			</level>
		</gather>
		
		<gather name="肉鸽练习屋">
			<level name="deathTrain">
				<info enemyLv="10" modeDiy="death" noRestartB="1" noTreasureB="1" noAIB="1" overWarn="退出后，等你再次回来时，你将回到研究室。" />
				<drop noB="1"/>
				<sceneLabel>QingMing</sceneLabel>
				<unitG>
					<allDefault aiOrder="patrolGlobal" noSuperB="1"></allDefault>
					<unitOrder id="enemy2" camp="enemy">
						<unit cnName="投毒僵尸" num="3" />
					</unitOrder>
				</unitG>
				
				<eventG>
					<group id="group1" cnName="事件集1">
						<event>
							<condition doNumber="1">liveEnemyNumber:less_1</condition>
							<order>createUnit:enemy2; r123</order>
							<order>allBody:enemy; farP1Spider:800</order>
						</event>
					</group>
				</eventG>
				
			</level>
		</gather>
		
		<gather name="肉鸽实验室">
			<level name="deathLab">
				<info enemyLv="10" modeDiy="death" noRestartB="1"  noTreasureB="1" noAIB="1" overWarn="退出后，等你再次回来时，你将重新回到这个研究室。" />
				<drop noB="1"/>
				<sceneLabel>YanJiuB</sceneLabel>
				<eventG>
					<group id="labFirst" cnName="第一次来">
						<event><!-- 添加p1生化罐 -->
							<condition>modeDiyString:labFirst</condition>
							<order>delEventGroupExcludeMe</order>
							<order>heroNoExistXY:1500,1160</order>
							<order>addTouch:humanCon; 1500,1160:p1,p1Con</order>
						</event>
						<event><!-- 使用生化罐 -->
							<condition delay="0.25" />
							<order>heroNoExistXY:1500,1160</order>
							<order>keyTouchId:p1Con</order>
						</event>
						<event><!-- 开启对话 -->
							<condition delay="2" />
							<order>say; startList:deathSay_lab1</order>
						</event>
					</group>
					
					<group id="mid" cnName="中间来">
						<event>
							<condition>modeDiyString:lab</condition>
							<order>delEventGroupExcludeMe</order>
						</event>
						<event>
							<condition delay="1"></condition>
							<order>say; startList:deathSay_lab1</order>
						</event>
					</group>
					
					<group id="labWin" cnName="通关">
						<event>
							<condition>modeDiyString:labWin</condition>
							<order>delEventGroupExcludeMe</order>
							<order>showMultiplySightCover:9999999; 3</order>
							<order>addTouch:humanConZero; 1300,1160:p1</order>
						</event>
						<event>
							<condition delay="1"></condition>
							<order>say; startList:deathSay_lab1</order>
							<order>body:p1; moveSpeedMul:0.5</order>
						</event>
					</group>
				</eventG>
			</level>
		</gather>
		
		<level name="deathLab">
			<![CDATA[首次 deep:0 die:0 win:0]]>
			<sayList name="first">
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>头好晕啊！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>这是哪里？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这里是克隆体研究室。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我为什么会在这？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>因为你是克隆体。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>怎么可能？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我记得我刚来霞光市不久。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你想起来了？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>看来记忆同步成功了！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我要离开这，出口在哪里？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>就在前面，不过你很快就会回来的。</content></say>
			</sayList>
			<![CDATA[第一次死后  deep:0 die:1 win:0]]>
			<sayList name="firstDie">
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>好疼啊！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>刚才是怎么回事？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>根据记忆信号显示，上一个你应该已经死了。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>刚才我确实重伤倒地……</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>所以我为你克隆了一具新的躯体，并传入你最新的记忆数据。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我的记忆？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>每具克隆体的大脑里都植入有记忆芯片，我们可以远程实时获取你的记忆。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>只要记忆还在，那你就是还是你。至于躯体是哪一具，就不重要了。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我真是克隆体？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>是的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我……我不能接受……</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>没关系，慢慢你就会接受的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我刚才收集的那些物品呢？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你都死了，你觉得那些东西还能带回来吗？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>唉，这次我得小心点了！</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>加油吧。</content></say>
			</sayList>
			
			
			<![CDATA[第1次 通关第1层  deep:1 die:任意 win:0]]>
			<sayList name="first1">
				<say target="流亡者"><content>恭喜你，通过了第一层。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我怎么又回到了这里？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这样你才能到下一层。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>通过下一层就能出去了吗？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这里一共有5层。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>不过在去之前，你最好把收集的血浆用完。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>血浆有什么用？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>可以强化你的某些能力，这些能力在死后还能得以保留。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我试试看。</content></say>
			</sayList>
			
			<![CDATA[第1次 通关第2层  deep:2 die:任意 win:0]]>
			<sayList name="first2">
				<say target="流亡者"><content>恭喜你，又通过了一层。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>有没有觉得自己变强了？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>有那么一点点。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>为什么外面的世界变成这样？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>什么样？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>只能通过传送门进行连接。还有这些传送门是从哪里来的？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>具体我也不清楚，因为我所处的世界还是正常的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>你是说我刚才所到的并非真实世界？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这是我的猜测。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你所在的研究室，我根本进不去，所以也无从查证。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>那你又是谁？为何会出现在这里？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>呵呵，等你通过了下一层，我再告诉你吧。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>好吧。</content></say>
				<![CDATA[
				<say target="流亡者"><content>坊间流传有2个版本。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>一个是这里遭到了外星人入侵，我觉得这个说法太奇葩了。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>另外一个呢？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>另外一个就是，这里有人使用过时光机，导致时空发生了紊乱。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>这都是什么跟什么啊？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>你是不是在骗我？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>我也只是听说而已。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我还是赶紧到下一层吧。</content></say>
				]]>
			</sayList>
			<![CDATA[第1次 通关第3层  deep:3 die:任意 win:0]]>
			<sayList name="first3">
				<say target="流亡者"><content>有没有觉得自己变强了？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>有那么一点点。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>我的身份其实没什么好隐瞒的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>那你说。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>我只是一名僵尸世界的流亡者而已。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>很久以前就听说，霞光市有座废弃的地下实验室，里头有你的克隆体。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>后来我来到这里，把这翻了个底朝天。历尽磨难，还真被我给找到了！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我的克隆体，有那么重要吗？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你的记忆还停留在过去，所以你并不知道，你的本体究竟有多强。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>有多强？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你是整个亚洲最强的战士之一。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>这么夸张吗？！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>那我现在怎么连这些僵尸都打得这么费劲？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>可能因为你只是克隆体吧？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>但即便是克隆体，我也认为你也拥有同等的能力，只是现在还没被激发出来而已。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>我想看看你是如何成长的，这也是我来这的目的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>原来如此。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>听完你这么一番话，我的身体里突然涌起了一股力量。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>嘿嘿！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>那为什么，这里会有我的克隆体？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你还不明白吗？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>造这座实验室的人和你有同样的目的？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>不一定哦，他们可能是想操控你。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>如此阴险？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你看这天花板……</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>太黑了，看不见啊。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>上面全是你的克隆体胚胎。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>啊！好可怕！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我还是赶紧走吧！</content></say>
			</sayList>
			
			<sayList name="first4">
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>感觉有点头晕。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>可能是有点累了吧。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>应该没什么大碍，我还是继续吧。</content></say>
			</sayList>
			<![CDATA[第1次 通关第5层  deep:5 die:任意 win:1 这时候win已经+1了]]>
			<sayList name="first5">
				<say target="流亡者"><content>恭喜你，通过了最后一层！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>为什么我感到全身无力……</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>也许是因为流了一些血。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>心脏跳得好厉害……</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我……我快要站不住了……</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>唉……看来目前的克隆体只能撑到第五层。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>什么意思？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你的寿命只有这么长……</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>不过已经比上次长了一些了。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>那我现在该怎么办？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>先去把血浆用完。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>然后进入这个生化罐，我会想办法保全你的躯体。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>只能这样了吗？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>是的。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>经过这几天的观察，克隆体的寿命会随着战斗经验的累积，而不断延长。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>所以你还是有希望的！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>好吧，现在也只能这样了！</content></say>
			</sayList>
			
			
			<![CDATA[通关后第一次  win:1 deep:0]]>
			<sayList name="s1_0">
				<say target="流亡者"><content>欢迎回来。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>看来我那具躯体并没有保住。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>我已经尽力了。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>算了，这事可能还是得靠我自己。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>加油吧！</content></say>
			</sayList>
			
			<sayList name="s1_1">
				<say target="流亡者"><content>很明显，现在的你比之前更强了。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>我也这么觉得。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>你那能看到这个研究室一共有多少具克隆体吗？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这边后台的确有数据。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>……大概 100具。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>这么多？！</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这还不包括已经死掉的克隆体。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>死掉的有多少？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>我看看……</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>……2596具。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>什么！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>那这些克隆体尸体都去哪了？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>在以前，这里的机器会通过地下管道，把尸体直接排到了东山澳的海里。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>不可想象！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>可是，我之前去过猪头洋，没有发现尸体或臭味什么的？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>你的记忆还停留在以前，那时的猪头洋的确是干净的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>现在呢？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>现在其实说来也没啥异样，我只是觉得那里的海水有点浑浊，不知道是不是心理作用。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>也许是这套机器有着独特处理尸体的方法吧。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>目前需要我摸索的地方还很多。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>你能关掉这个管道吗？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>事实上，为了避免被别人发现这个实验室，我早就把它给关了。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>目前尸体都是直接火化处理，只不过废气的排放还有些问题。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>那就好，我可不想让别人看到我的尸体。</content></say>
			</sayList>
			<sayList name="s1_2">
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>流亡者！</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>怎么了？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>既然有那么多死掉的克隆体，那说明他们已经实验了很多次了。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>是的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>应该取得了一定的成果吧。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>我这里的确有一份实验日志，不过是残缺的。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>有没有实验出正常寿命的克隆体？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>有的，一共有两具。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>还有真有？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这两具克隆体不仅有正常的人类寿命，还有超强的战斗能力，被标注上了“S级”字样。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>不过日志上还写着，其中一具已经失踪了。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>另外一具呢？</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>这里没写。</content></say>
				<say target="流亡者"><content>不过这个实验室已经废弃，根据损坏的痕迹来看，之前也发生过激烈的战斗。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>唉，不知道这两具克隆体现在在哪。</content></say>
				
			</sayList>
			<sayList name="s1_3">
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>流亡者！</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>出来，有事问题你呢。</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>他人呢？</content></say>
				<say target="deathPlayer"><content>怎么突然消失了……</content></say>
			</sayList>
		</level>
	</father>
</data>